g.text: Percentage of population reporting they never wear a mask in Victoria declined rapidly to zero when mask-wearing became
mandatory. Other states with lesser or no outbreak report much less mask wearing, reflecting what we know to be reality.
University of Maryland Global Symptom Survey of Facebook users, analysed at http://freerangestats.info
